Report is a web application based on the play framework : http://www.playframework.org/

It is a simple application, to handle report edition better than a wiki page.
Features:
 * Concurrent edition
 * Report shown as tree
 * Send reminders to people who are not yet completed his report part
 * Send reports by email 
 * History section containing all past reports


